[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]57%[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]say services being
[normal] centralised, so clients have to travel further to get help
[normal]77%[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]identified specific groups that are losing out – the main ones being disabled, elderly and black and minority ethnic people
[normal]38%[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]of staff said their employers were prioritising services on cont
[normal]racts to public bodies over campaigning and 
[normal]advocacy
